        <h1 class="content-left green">Wiki Icon Images.</h1>
        <p>The image that represents a wiki under any given category is chosen based on the image you upload when editing your wiki. Additional images can of course be uploaded using Markdown, but you choose the image that will be displayed when another user explores the category that your wiki is under.</p>
      </div>
